<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0312347294" class="internal">ISBN 0312347294</a> (10) and <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780312347291" class="internal">ISBN 978-0312347291</a> (13)</td>
</tr>
